"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130132840SCyHM5k1RAU0rP2g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/2019-pre-fall/new-york/31-phillip-lim/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">3.1 Phillip Lim 发布 2019 早秋系列：</a></strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130132944I7Vcj1Wf8vaKoysR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499023\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130132948DOIiaLYHeWx1pEtX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130132949FVHqMhlB7RwfgWPY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.dazeddigital.com/fashion/article/42162/1/models-stretch-it-out-wearing-the-newest-chunky-new-balance-608\" rel=\"nofollow\"><em>Dazed</em> 为&nbsp;New Balance 608 新配色的发布拍摄了一组造型特辑。</a></strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130134300WpH294YoKxIQOya8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.427344\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130134301dLIojBK04STX6J1C.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130134255tp89RQ4qmhCauNr1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130134253A6xBECrfgOeRHiFQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130134254zO1E9vPaTR4NQcDI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.637500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130134255aN5wxR9K0TD4CtlS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130134259e9JZgRtSdrYHvhiI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.637500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>摄影展<em>“</em><a href=\"http://www.howardgreenberg.com/exhibitions/vivian-maier-the-color-work?view=slider\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vivian Maier: The Colour Work</a><em>”</em>将在纽约&nbsp;Howard Greenberg Gallery 展出至 2019 年 1 月 5 日。</p><p>Vivian Maier（1926–2009）是芝加哥的一名普通保姆，业余爱好是摄影。导演 John Maloof 在 2007 年的一次拍卖会上偶然买到了她的作品，将它们上传到网上，并于 2005 年拍摄了一部获得奥斯卡提名的纪录片“<em><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8ZoYG1kgMNo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Finding Vivian Maier</a>”&nbsp;</em>。此次展览中，你将看到 Vivian Maier 较为少见的彩色摄影作品。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130135010qgBIWM6GjXwET42b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130135010qcC9RHMw58iLVx3U.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130135001cheLgbYsnHEAfQPW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.468519\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130135000Hf9TKUolFNbG4tPw.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.500781\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130135002z07piqe5SKsQGOWl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130135009kOVc2gvdtGRfxIj8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130134956NYLIPMoyOrcdhXZz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.681250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130134958Z1pue3YrXEgzPqBf.JPG\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130134959AePa7CFJRcSDTnvw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130135000VMvCJDqdIgzUKLfZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130134959mcZBwERg4Ga3CdnS.JPG\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130135002p6VOdsSHxuZmB8wa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.681250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181130135003TVqgr2w7ocypBK9x.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.676562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图为&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.anothermag.com/art-photography/11345/vivian-maier-the-colour-work-photography-exhibition-howard-greenberg-gallery\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vivian Maier 摄影作品</a></p>"}